Titolo: Heat Signature (video game)

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Heat Signature is an action stealth video game developed and published in 2017 by Suspicious Developments, the studio behind 2013's Gunpoint. The player plays as a mercenary who takes on missions around a procedurally generated galaxy in order to liberate space stations. Heat Signature launched for Microsoft Windows on September 21, 2017.

Genere: Action 

Valutazione: N/A
